  "special": {
    "description": "Consumes 1 ammo per shot but fires 3 projectiles.\n\nThe bullet pattern forms a smiling face (two eyes and a grin) and shifts from tight, to wide, then tight again.\n\nMoxxi weapon effect: while held, you gain 4% life steal from all damage you deal.",
    "title": "We're all mad here. I'm mad. You're mad."
  },
  "notes": "Gaige can exploit Kitten with Close Enough, as its high fire rate and multiple projectiles per ammo help spray ricochets. Anarchy further reduces practical range and can throw rounds far outside the reticle.\n\nAs a Moxxi weapon it always rolls an element and returns health when you deal damage.\n\nKrieg pairs well with it at close range. Hellborn skills can improve elemental synergy and healing, while Bloodlust skills benefit from its ammo efficiency and large magazine.",
